<HEADLINE> Jordan's Stock Market Index Lower </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
AMMAN, June 3 (Xinhua) -- Price index on the Amman Financial
Market (AFM), Jordan's sole stock market, closed at 174.90
Wednesday, 2.06 points lower than Tuesday.
</P>
<P>
The AFM daily report said the turnover was 2,027,647 Jordanian
dinars (about 2,863,908 U.S. dollars).
</P>
<P>
A total of 997,435 shares changed hands in 682 contracts.
</P>
