Turkey will abide by all the agreements it has signed with the
international community in a determined manner, the statement said.
</P>
<P>
It also expressed grave concern over the nuclear tests that
India and Pakistan conducted in the past weeks, saying that these
irresponsible acts might lead to a nuclear arms race in the
southern Asia. 
