inside Eritrea over the past few days: on May 22, 23 and 25 in
Setit area, and on May 31 in the Aiga-Aliteina areas."
</P>
<P>
The international community has pursued mediations between the
two countries since the Ethiopian government termed an invasion
of the Ethiopian locality of Badme and part of Sheraro by
Eritrean forces on May 12, this year. 
