of agriculture, cooperatives and land reclamation -- were not
filled.
</P>
<P>
There had been some restructuring of portfolios, including the
establishement of the Ministry of Environment, Women and Youth
Affairs. This will be handled by the only female member of the
cabinet, Mamoshebi Kabi.
</P>
