Palace in Maseru Thursday morning.
</P>
<P>
The names of Prime Minister Pakalitha Mosisili, and Leketekete
Ketso, minister of finance and development planning, Mopshatla
Mabitle, minister of local government and home affairs, Tom
Thabane, minister of foreign Affairs are found in the 14 members
cabinet.
</P>
<P>
The cabinet was formed after the LCD won a sweeping victory in
the May 23 general election. 
</P>
