times while Davenport broke the third seed seven times after
earning 13 break points.
</P>
<P>
The American, who was bidding for a place in her first Grand
Slam final, made a better start to the second-set as she broke her
opponent to a 2-0 lead before Sanchez Vicario came back to the
match.
</P>
<P>
Davenport continued to go for big winners and although guilty
of over-hitting, she managed to climb back to 4-4 and then forced
a tie-break where Sanchez Vicario recovered from 3-5 to edge
home. 
