<HEADLINE> Australia-U.S. Defense Treaty Extended </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
CANBERRA, June 4 (Xinhua) -- The Pine Gap defense treaty
between Australia and the United States has been extended for a
further 10 years.
</P>
<P>
