<HEADLINE> Israeli Soldier Wounded in South Lebanon </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BEIRUT, June 4 (Xinhua) -- An Israeli solider was seriously
wounded Wednesday night when his armored personnel carrier hit a
roadside bomb in south Lebanon, Voice of the People radio here
reported Thursday.
</P>
<P>
The explosion took place near the village of Bint Jubiel in the
central part of the Israeli occupied zone.
</P>
<P>
