<HEADLINE> Over 1,100 Die in Riots in Indonesia Last Month </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
JAKARTA, June 4 (Xinhua) -- Over 1,100 people died in rioting
in Jakarta and other parts of Indonesia from May 12 to 25,
newspapers Thursday quoted the National Commission on Human Rights
as saying.
</P>
<P>
