preliminary round matches, and around 5,300 spectators were
counted at the second round in Berlin and 6,173 in Bermen. A total
of 2,906 fans watched the classification matches at Dessau.
</P>
<P>
At this world basketball championship only day tickets were
sold. During the inermediate round the tickets were valid for
three matches per day, the organizers added. 
